<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" style="margin: 0; padding: 0;">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333333;
        }
        .container {
            width: 100%;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 8px;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            border: 2px solid #007bff;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #007bff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .content h2 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #007bff;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .content p {
            margin: 0 0 20px;
            font-weight: 400;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #777777;
            border-top: 1px solid #dddddd;
            font-weight: 400;
        }
        p{
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #2c2c2c
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
            <img src=" " alt=" Logo" height="60px">
            <h1>ABC Company</h1>
            <h1>Return Book Request Notification</h1>
        </div>
    

    <div class="content">
    <p>Dear Librarian,</p>
    <p>A new Return request has been submitted. I have done my work with this book. So I want return the book back to the library.</p>
      <p><strong>Borrower Name:</strong> {{borrower_name}}</p>
      <p><strong>Register ID:</strong> {{register_id}}</p>
      <p><strong>Book Title:</strong> {{title}}</p>
      <p><strong>Borrower Email:</strong> {{borrower_email}}</p>
      <p><strong>Borrow Date:</strong> {{borrow_date}}</p>
      <p><strong>Return Date:</strong> {{return_date}}</p>
      <p>If you need any further details, please do not hesitate to contact us.</p>
      
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      2024 Library Management System. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
